  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so it happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't run away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were two guys and two guys [? were there. ?] If I'm not success, you jump in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we took the sticks from this wagon that hold it, took apart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went around this when he's sleeping and the other guy around this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I miss, you go, you hit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we killed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we ran out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the field was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To bring water up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyway, that's how I remember it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we behind the whole thing in the field, we all 50-- or 45, I don't know-- were laying a whole night in the field, a whole day in the field.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And next day, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we saw-- we're laying still, not eating, no-- no we [? chew-- ?] the-- the [INAUDIBLE] [LAUGHS] was going there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we saw the farmer looking for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he didn't know, he was stupid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't know if we went away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We hide the guy, the-- the policeman, this-- this soldier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we pulled him with us into the field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he probably thought that we all went with him away our barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jeep-- the driver sits in the Jeep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the guy with the machine gun in the side sits in the back ready with the machine gun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know these Americans, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he goes and he turns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're going slowly because each time they're going in, they're afraid that they're being attacked, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just-- they went forward, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So a Jeep. 10 minutes later, I see a command car with a big machine in the middle.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
